OL,3,CGloria Hunniford 'delighted' to
OL,4,Creceive Freedom of the City of London
OL,6,FBroadcaster Gloria Hunniford has said
OL,7,Fshe is "delighted and humbled" to
OL,8,Freceive the Freedom of the City of
OL,9,FLondon.
OL,11,FThe 86-year-old's long and varied
OL,12,Fcareer has seen her host chat shows
OL,13,Fand current affairs, lifestyle and
OL,14,Fconsumer rights programmes.
OL,16,FShe was awarded the Freedom of the
OL,17,FCity of London at the city's Guildhall
OL,18,Fon Thursday in recognition of her
OL,19,F"outstanding contribution to
OL,20,Fentertainment and campaigning work as
OL,21,Fa breast cancer charity ambassador".
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@^O]{D@AOU}D@cO]
