PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779019866
OL,3,CGloria Hunniford 'delighted' to
OL,4,Creceive Freedom of the City of London
OL,6,FAs well as her TV work, she is known
OL,7,Ffor setting up the Caron Keating
OL,8,FFoundation in memory of her daughter,
OL,9,Fwho died from breast cancer in 2004.
OL,11,FBorn in Portadown, Northern Ireland,
OL,12,Fin 1982 Hunniford became the first
OL,13,Fwoman to have her own daily radio show
OL,14,Fon BBC Radio 2.
OL,16,FShe presented it continuously for 13
OL,17,Fyears, before going on to become one
OL,18,Fof the first female broadcasters to
OL,19,Fhost her own TV chat show.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779019866
OL,3,CGloria Hunniford 'delighted' to
OL,4,Creceive Freedom of the City of London
OL,6,FHer many TV credits include Pebble
OL,7,FMill At One, Good Evening Ulster, The
OL,8,FTravelling Picture Show, Rip-Off
OL,9,FBritain, Loose Women, Strictly Come
OL,10,FDancing, This Morning, The One Show,
OL,11,FPiers Morgan's Life Stories, This Is
OL,12,FYour Life, and The Masked Singer.
OL,14,FShe was awarded an OBE for services to
OL,15,Fcancer charities through breast
OL,16,Fscreening services and cancer support
OL,17,Fin 2017.
OL,19,FHer autobiography, My Life, was
OL,20,Fpublished a year later.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
