FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779019866
OL,3,CGloria Hunniford 'delighted' to
OL,4,Creceive Freedom of the City of London
OL,6,FSpeaking after Thursday's ceremony,
OL,7,FHunniford said: "This has been an
OL,8,Fextremely special and memorable day
OL,9,Ffor me and my family.
OL,11,F"Some of my most treasured moments in
OL,12,Fbroadcasting have taken place in this
OL,13,Fcity, so I am delighted and humbled to
OL,14,Fhave received the Freedom of the City
OL,15,Fof London."
OL,17,FHunniford said she began her career
OL,18,Faged just six, when she sang as a
OL,19,Fchild performer.
OL,26,@oD@QOUsD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779019866
OL,3,CGloria Hunniford 'delighted' to
OL,4,Creceive Freedom of the City of London
OL,6,F"Singing from that tender age led me
OL,7,Fto a career in broadcasting, which I
OL,8,Fwas given back in 1969 at the
OL,9,Fbeginning of the Troubles," she added.
OL,11,F"Ultimately, that experience led to
OL,12,Fbeing given yet another wonderful
OL,13,Fbroadcasting opportunity with BBC
OL,14,FRadio 2, which I did daily for 13
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,F"Television followed, from my own chat
OL,18,Fshow, ITV's Sunday Sunday, to Heaven
OL,19,FAnd Earth, Rip Off Britain, and Loose
OL,20,FWomen."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@[O]sD@AOUyD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
