OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779019866
OL,3,CGloria Hunniford 'delighted' to
OL,4,Creceive Freedom of the City of London
OL,6,FHunniford took part in the BBC's
OL,7,FStrictly Come Dancing in 2005, where
OL,8,Fshe was partnered by professional
OL,9,Fdancer Darren Bennett and eliminated
OL,10,Fin the third week.
OL,12,FShe lost her husband of more than 20
OL,13,Fyears, Stephen Way, in 2024 and said
OL,14,Fhe had left "the most enormous void,
OL,15,Fnot only in my life".
OL,17,FLast year, she took part in The Great
OL,18,FCelebrity Bake Off For Stand Up To
OL,19,FCancer.
OL,26,@vD@MOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
