OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779019866
OL,3,CGloria Hunniford 'delighted' to
OL,4,Creceive Freedom of the City of London
OL,6,FCity of London Corporation policy
OL,7,Fchairman, Chris Hayward, said: "A
OL,8,Fconsummate professional on our screens
OL,9,Fand airwaves, millions of us have been
OL,10,Fentertained, informed, and moved by
OL,11,FGloria Hunniford over the years.
OL,13,F"It has been a pleasure for my
OL,14,Fcolleagues to welcome Gloria to
OL,15,FGuildhall for her admission into the
OL,16,FFreedom today."
OL,26,@oD@`OUuD@AOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779019866
OL,3,CGloria Hunniford 'delighted' to
OL,4,Creceive Freedom of the City of London
OL,6,FAlderman Vincent Keaveny said: "As
OL,7,FGovernor of The Honourable The Irish
OL,8,FSociety, the City of London's historic
OL,9,Flink with Ulster, and now a cross-
OL,10,Fcommunity charity in Northern Ireland,
OL,11,Fit is a real pleasure to nominate
OL,12,FGloria for the Freedom of the City of
OL,13,FLondon.
OL,15,F"She has been a wonderful
OL,16,Frepresentative of Northern Ireland on
OL,17,FTV and radio for many years, bringing
OL,18,Fmuch joy and happiness into the lives
OL,19,Fof her audience.
OL,26,@nD@`OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779019866
OL,3,CGloria Hunniford 'delighted' to
OL,4,Creceive Freedom of the City of London
OL,6,F"Her work for cancer charities was
OL,7,Fhonoured with her OBE, but that work
OL,8,Fcontinues and it is right that we also
OL,9,Fcelebrate it today.
OL,11,F"Thank you, Gloria, for all that you
OL,12,Fhave given us."
OL,14,FVince Dignam, business performance and
OL,15,Ftransport group manager at the City of
OL,16,FLondon Corporation, said: "Gloria has
OL,17,Fbeen a part of our lives as a
OL,18,Fhousehold name and TV personality for
OL,19,Fyears and she is undoubtedly a
OL,20,Fnational treasure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@OO]xD@[OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
