OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779019866
OL,3,CGloria Hunniford 'delighted' to
OL,4,Creceive Freedom of the City of London
OL,6,F"I got to know Gloria through her
OL,7,Fcharity work and she has been a true
OL,8,Finspiration in raising vital funds for
OL,9,Fcancer charities and supporting one of
OL,10,Fmy charities personally by attending
OL,11,Fevents.
OL,13,F"I was proud to nominate this amazing
OL,14,Flady for the Freedom of the City of
OL,15,FLondon ` it is very much deserved."
OL,17,FOne of the City of London's ancient
OL,18,Ftraditions, the Freedom is believed to
OL,19,Fhave begun in 1237 and enabled
OL,20,Frecipients to carry out their trade.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
