PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779019866
OL,3,CGloria Hunniford 'delighted' to
OL,4,Creceive Freedom of the City of London
OL,6,FAs well as being nominated for, or
OL,7,Fapplying for, the Freedom, it is also
OL,8,Foffered by the City of London
OL,9,FCorporation to individuals as a way of
OL,10,Fpaying tribute to their outstanding
OL,11,Fcontribution to London or public life,
OL,12,For to celebrate a very significant
OL,13,Fachievement.
OL,15,FRecent recipients include actor Ray
OL,16,FWinstone and City of London Police
OL,17,FSpecial Constable and TV presenter,
OL,18,FPenny Lancaster.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/12
